com.conorthomason.garageapp

Class Garage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.conorthomason.garageapp.Garage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Garage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Garage class stores the spaces, vehicles, and space counts of the Garage. Allows input/removal of appropriate objects.
